[[ch01-getting-started]]
== Getting Started

This chapter will be about getting started with Taiko.

We will begin by explaining some history on browser testing, how Taiko is different, then move on to how to get Taiko running on your system.

At the end of this chapter you should understand why Taiko is around, install it and record your first test script.

include::book/01-introduction/sections/about-taiko.asc[]

=== Summary

You should have a basic understanding of Taiko and it's API with a simple test.
It's now time to understand other API's and features for testing more complex
functionalities. 
